data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value:
select h.PurchaseChallan_Id as 'Id',(select ISNULL(cnt_firstName,'')+' '+ISNULL(cnt_middleName,'')+' '+ISNULL(cnt_lastName,'') from tbl_master_contact where cnt_internalId=h.PurchaseChallan_VendorId) as 'Customer',h.PurchaseChallan_FinYear as 'Doc_FinYear',h.PurchaseChallan_Number as 'Doc_no',h.PurchaseChallan_Date as 'Doc_date',(select branch_description from tbl_master_branch where branch_id=h.PurchaseChallan_BranchId) as 'Branch' --,h.Challan_TotalAmount as 'Total Net Amount' , ,ISNULL((select sum(Challan_TotalAmountInLocalCurrency) from tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanDetails where PurchaseChallanId=h.PurchaseChallan_Id),0) + ISNULL((select sum(ChallanTax_Amount) from tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanTax where ChallanTax_ChallanId=h.PurchaseChallan_Id),0) as 'Total Net Amount' ,
Cast(ISNULL((select sum(Challan_TotalAmountInLocalCurrency) from tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanDetails where PurchaseChallanId=h.PurchaseChallan_Id),0) + ISNULL((select sum(ChallanTax_Amount) from tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanTax where ChallanTax_ChallanId=h.PurchaseChallan_Id),0) as decimal(18,2)) as 'Format Total Net Amount' ,
c.CNT_GSTIN,pan_no=(select crg_Number from tbl_master_contactRegistration where crg_cntId=c.cnt_internalId and crg_type ='Pan Card') ,(select user_name from tbl_master_user where user_id=h.CreatedBy) as 'user_name' from tbl_trans_PurchaseChallan h inner join tbl_master_contact c on h.PurchaseChallan_VendorId=c.cnt_internalId where h.PurchaseChallan_Id=@PChallan_id

data.name: customSqlQuery2.Sql
data.value:
select Id,relation_Id,Product_Name,Product_Id,Product_Description,barcode_itemslno,Quantity,Unit,Rate,Amount,Total_Amount,Isnull(ProdWise_TaxAmt,0) as ProdWise_TaxAmt,(Total_Amount+Isnull(ProdWise_TaxAmt,0)) as prodTaxTotAmt ,Is_Taxpresent=ISNULL(( select top 1 ProductTax_TaxTypeId from tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanDetailsProductTax where ProductTax_ChallanId=@PChallan_id and ProductTax_ProductId=Product_Id),0) from
( select ChallanDetails_Id as 'Id',PurchaseChallanId as 'relation_Id',(select sProducts_Name from Master_sProducts where sProducts_ID=ChallanDetails_ProductId) as 'Product_Name',ChallanDetails_ProductId as 'Product_Id', ChallanDetails_ProductDescription as 'Product_Description', (select sProducts_barCode from Master_sProducts where sProducts_ID=tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanDetails.ChallanDetails_ProductId) as 'barcode_itemslno', ChallanDetails_Quantity as 'Quantity',(select UOM_ShortName from Master_UOM where UOM_ID=tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanDetails.ChallanDetails_UOMId) as 'Unit',Details_PurchasePrice as 'Rate',Details_Amount as 'Amount',Challan_TotalAmountInLocalCurrency as 'Total_Amount',
ProdWise_TaxAmt=(select sum(ProductTax_Amount) from tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanDetailsProductTax where ProductTax_ChallanId=@PChallan_id and ProductTax_ProductId=tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanDetails.ChallanDetails_Id and (ProductTax_Percentage!=0 or ProductTax_Amount!=0))
from tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanDetails where PurchaseChallanId=@PChallan_id ) details

data.name: customSqlQuery3.Sql
data.value:
select ChallanAdd_ChallanId as 'relation_Id',
(select ChallanAdd_address1+case when ChallanAdd_address2='' then '' else +','+ChallanAdd_address2 end +case when ChallanAdd_address3='' then '' else +','+ChallanAdd_address3 end +case when ChallanAdd_landMark='' then '' else +','+ChallanAdd_landMark end ) as 'Address',
ChallanAdd_address1 as 'Address1',ChallanAdd_address2 as 'Address2',ChallanAdd_address3 as 'Address3',ChallanAdd_landMark as 'landMark',(select cou_country from tbl_master_country where cou_id=tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanAddress.ChallanAdd_countryId) as 'Country', (select state from tbl_master_state where id=tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanAddress.ChallanAdd_stateId) as 'State',(select RTrim(LTrim(city_name))+' :' from tbl_master_city where city_id=tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanAddress.ChallanAdd_cityId) as 'City',(select area_name from tbl_master_area where area_id=tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanAddress.ChallanAdd_areaId) as 'Area',ChallanAdd_pin as 'Pin' from tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanAddress where ChallanAdd_ChallanId=@PChallan_id and ChallanAdd_addressType='Billing'

data.name: customSqlQuery4.Sql
data.value: select ProductTax_Id as 'Id',ProductTax_ChallanId as 'relation_Id',cast(ProductTax_ProductId as bigint) as 'ProductId',ProductTax_TaxTypeId,(select TaxRatesSchemeName from Config_TaxRates where TaxRates_ID=tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanDetailsProductTax.ProductTax_TaxTypeId) as 'ProductTax_TaxTypeName',ProductTax_Percentage,ProductTax_Amount, (select TaxRatesSchemeName from Config_TaxRates where TaxRates_ID=tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanDetailsProductTax.ProductTax_TaxTypeId)+' '+cast((CONVERT(DECIMAL(10,0),ProductTax_Percentage)) as varchar(20))+'%' +' '+cast(ProductTax_Amount as varchar(50)) as 'Tax',(cast((CONVERT(DECIMAL(10,0),ProductTax_Percentage)) as varchar(20))+'%') as tax_percnt from tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanDetailsProductTax where ProductTax_ChallanId=@PChallan_id and (ProductTax_Percentage!=0 or ProductTax_Amount!=0)

data.name: customSqlQuery5.Sql
data.value: select Id,relation_Id ,Percentage,Amount,TaxTypeId,Tax_Name=(select Taxes_Name from Master_Taxes where taxes_Id=(select TaxRates_TaxCode from Config_TaxRates where TaxRates_ID=TaxTypeId)) from ( select ChallanTax_Id as 'Id',ChallanTax_ChallanId as 'relation_Id',ChallanTax_Percentage as 'Percentage',ChallanTax_Amount as 'Amount',ChallanTax_TaxTypeId as 'TaxTypeId' from tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanTax where (ChallanTax_TaxTypeId<>0 or ProductTax_VatGstCstId<>0)) aa where relation_Id=@PChallan_id and Amount<>0

data.name: customSqlQuery6.Sql
data.value:
select c.*,phone=(select top 1 phf_phoneNumber from tbl_master_phonefax where phf_cntId=c.cmp_internalid),email=(select top 1 eml_email from tbl_master_email where eml_cntId=c.cmp_internalid) ,
ISNULL(a.add_address1,'')+', '+ISNULL(a.add_address2,'')+', '+ISNULL(a.add_address3,'')+', '+case when (select ISNULL(city_name,'') from tbl_master_city where city_id=a.add_city)<>'' then (select ISNULL(city_name,'') from tbl_master_city where city_id=a.add_city)+'-'+(select pin_code from tbl_master_pinzip where pin_id=a.add_pin)+'.' else '' end as 'Address',
(select city_name from tbl_master_city where city_id=a.add_city)as add_city,(select pin_code from tbl_master_pinzip where pin_id=a.add_pin) as add_pin from tbl_master_company c inner join tbl_master_address a on c.cmp_internalid=a.add_cntId where c.cmp_internalid=@Company_Id

data.name: customSqlQuery7.Sql
data.value: select ProductTax_ChallanId as 'relation_Id',sum(ProductTax_Amount) as ProductTax_Amount, mode=(select TaxCalculateMethods from Master_Taxes where Taxes_ID=(select TaxRates_TaxCode from Config_TaxRates where TaxRates_ID=tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanDetailsProductTax.ProductTax_TaxTypeId)) , TaxRatesSchemeName=(select TaxRatesSchemeName from Config_TaxRates where TaxRates_ID=tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanDetailsProductTax.ProductTax_TaxTypeId) from tbl_trans_PurchaseChallanDetailsProductTax where ProductTax_ChallanId=@PChallan_id and (ProductTax_Percentage!=0 or ProductTax_Amount!=0) group by ProductTax_TaxTypeId,ProductTax_ChallanId
